// ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
// Created:     29 July 2008 by cnwab1
//
// Purpose:     
//
// Parameters:  None
//
// Returns:     Nothing
//
// Changed On   	Changed By  	Reason
// ----------   	----------  	--------------------------------------------------
// 14/10/2009		cnwdap1			PAR #21334 Make release form non-modal
// 27/02/2014		cnwdap1			PAR #33582 Allow Security Gate visits without a registration number
// 14/05/2018		jlgdap1			TFS 38501 PEL1 Work Order Changes
