Purpose:			

Parameters:			

Return Value:		

Date		Who		Reason
20 Nov 2024	navah1	Bug 32770: CUX - Road Gate - Search is not working when a truck with a similar license plate is already on terminal

*/

vars

begin
	self.onRegChanged();
	if self.cmbRegNo.listObject &lt;&gt; null then
			self.detailsChangedVehicle := true;
	endif;
epilog

end;</source>
